import React, { useState,useEffect } from "react"; import { useParams, Link, useLocation } from "react-router-dom"; import moment from 'moment'; import movies from "../movies" function Booking(props) { var days = [ {id:0, date:moment().add(0, "days").format("ddd, MMM D"),}, {id:1, date:moment().add(1, "days").format("ddd, MMM D"),}, {id:2, date:moment().add(2, "days").format("ddd, MMM D"),} ]; const params = useParams(); const userId = params.movie; const [count, setCount] = useState([0, false]); const obj = movies.find(function (num) { return num.title === userId; }); const [movie, setmovieData] = useState([]); const [found, setNotFound] = useState(null); const [flag,setflag]= useState([false]); useEffect(() => { fetch( `http://www.omdbapi.com/?t=${obj.title}&y=${obj.year}&apikey=961ea94b` ) .then((res) => res.json()) .then((data) => setmovieData(data)) .catch((err) => { setNotFound(true); }); }, []); function handleClick(data) { if (data.target.className === "seat") { data.target.className = "seat selected"; setCount([count[0] + 1, true]); } else { data.target.className = "seat"; let a = count[0] - 1; let b = false; if (a > 0) { b = true; } setCount([a, b]); } console.log(count); } function dateclick(data) { var cls=data.target.className; days.map((num)=>{ if(num.id===cls){ setflag(flag[num.id]==true) } else{ setflag(flag[num.id] == false); } }) } return ( <>
